x4freetext: Data taken from fig. 1a of the referenece
13C targets were made by cracking
acetylene enriched up to 80 % in 13C isotope. The
cracking was done in a high frequency discharge. The
polymer was allowed to deposit on 15 mu-g/cm carbon
foils or 0.12 pm nickel foils. By this method 13C
targets of thicknesses from 5 mu-g/cm to 20 mu-g/cm2
were prepared.
